### DECISION TOOLS

MODULE 10 — PERSONAL FINANCE CHATBOT
A conversational AI assistant with full access to your portfolio, live market data, your trade history, your goals, and the live news feed. Ask it anything in English or Hindi and it answers in the context of your specific financial situation. You can also send a screenshot of anything you don't understand — a confusing chart, a news headline, a financial statement — and the chatbot reads the image and explains it in plain language. Powered by Mistral-7B running locally — your financial data never leaves your device. The chatbot never tells you what to do. It gives you complete information and always ends with "the final decision is yours."

MODULE 11 — STOCK COMPARISON TOOL
Compare any two stocks side by side — price, PE ratio, one-year return, dividend yield, debt levels, volatility, and analyst consensus. AEGIS gives its own verdict at the bottom. And crucially — it tells you how adding either stock would specifically affect your current portfolio's sector balance and risk profile. Not generic comparison. Personalized comparison.

MODULE 12 — WATCHLIST WITH SMART ALERTS
Add stocks you're interested in but not ready to buy. Set your target entry price. Write your reason for watching it. AEGIS monitors it and alerts you when the price reaches your target — but also tells you whether the original reason you added it is still valid or whether something has changed in the fundamentals or sentiment around that stock. Most apps alert you when price hits. AEGIS alerts you when price hits AND the thesis is still intact.

MODULE 13 — REAL PROFIT CALCULATOR
Before you sell any stock, AEGIS shows your actual profit after every deduction — brokerage on both sides, STT (Securities Transaction Tax), GST on brokerage, SEBI charges, stamp duty, and tax. STCG at 20% if held under 12 months, LTCG at 12.5% if held over 12 months. It also tells you — if you wait X more days, you save Y rupees in tax. One feature that prevents thousands of rupees from silently disappearing on every trade.

