## THE TECHNOLOGY BEHIND AEGIS

PPO Reinforcement Learning Agent (PyTorch + Stable-Baselines3)
An AI agent trained on 20 years of market data using a reward and punishment system. Rewarded for generating advice that leads to good risk-adjusted returns. Punished for advice that leads to unnecessary losses. Like training a chess engine, but for portfolio advisory.

LSTM Neural Network (PyTorch)
A type of AI specifically designed to understand sequences over time — perfect for stock prices where what happened last week affects what happens today. Looks at 60 days of price data and forecasts short-term price direction.

Hidden Markov Model (hmmlearn)
Classifies the current market regime — Bull, Bear, or High Volatility — from price movements and volume data. AEGIS adjusts its advisory style based on which regime is detected.

FinBERT (HuggingFace)
An AI model pre-trained on financial news and analyst reports. Reads every news headline and social post and correctly interprets financial language — outputting a Bullish, Neutral, or Bearish score.

CVaR Engine (NumPy)
Calculates your portfolio's statistical worst-case loss threshold. Triggers the Recovery Engine only when something truly abnormal happens — not on normal bad days.

Monte Carlo Simulation (SciPy)
Runs 500 simulated recovery scenarios based on historical precedent. Generates probabilistic recovery timelines — honest probability ranges, not false certainty.

SHAP and Captum
Explainability tools that look inside the AI models and identify exactly which factor caused a specific outcome. Makes every AI decision fully transparent.

Mistral-7B via Ollama (Local LLM)
Open-source language model running entirely on your own device. Converts all complex math and data into plain English or Hindi. Your financial data never leaves your device.

Zerodha Kite Connect API
Read-only connection to your Demat account. AEGIS can see your holdings and history. It can never place orders or move money. Ever.

